title: TempEnd
---
The ride bus home was uneventful and cold. Walking home from the bus 
station was quiet, bar from the cars and people passing as they went on 
with their day. Your home was cold too, as was your dinner as you
felt even turning on the oven was more than needed.

You ate alone, before laying your head down at long last, 
thankful for one less day to worry about.

END OF BETA. PRESS 'R' TO RESTART.
